{"tid":1970333,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[高達]匯豐無息派事件|從基本面/現實說現金股息的重要性|股息投資法已老土過時了嗎?","createTime":"2020-04-13T05:30:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T04:35:28.000Z","uid":343020,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e2ba40dd1571c748755d2491d6fbd18d3b03125c","tid":1970333,"uid":343020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:30:06.000Z","msg":"大家好,又係我高達<br />\n<strong>匯豐無息派事件|從價值投資/財技面/實戰說現金股息的重要性|股息投資法已老土過時了嗎?</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8-mNrq2_sRs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8-mNrq2_sRs&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=b77defa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8-mNrq2_sRs</a><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n自問唔係專家，只係一些透過個人經驗不斷學習翻黎的心得和分享<br />\n我既目標係希望盡量幫香港人可以搜集一些實用/含經濟效益/搵到食既資料<br />\n計劃黎緊主要會上載既片/資源題材包括<br />\n求職/轉工<br />\n職業發展<br />\n進修〔搵下有冇啲可以幫大家有一技之長/移民(唔係冇選擇都唔鼓勵)加分既知識〕<br />\n其他實用野等等...稔到再整<br />\n<br />\n其他<br />\n移民可提早領強積金?! 香港有5萬個100萬強積金戶口?!點用「永久性地離開香港」做理由拎MPF？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8dDX7i-fJbM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8dDX7i-fJbM&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=0a2f816c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8dDX7i-fJbM</a>"},{"pid":"61bf2cfa7dc55837473dfc15e0903d023fc83eaf","tid":1970333,"uid":91813,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:36:23.000Z","msg":"一間真正有潛力既公司 你唔會希望佢派息"},{"pid":"d277c873da7a39d766f7474d9eba252503afbc56","tid":1970333,"uid":123704,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T07:16:59.000Z","msg":"要息不如買債，但而家個債市只係用QE頂住，值唔值得投資就要諗諗"},{"pid":"95ac88aeb40aace48e21214fc5b728cb65da4110","tid":1970333,"uid":33099,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"61bf2cfa7dc55837473dfc15e0903d023fc83eaf","tid":1970333,"uid":91813,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"cited